          <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="T_Menu">A Spline</text><text style="font-style:normal;"> is</text> a the one sketch-element in which we do not drag to add it to the graphic-area.</para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text">To add a Spline, we click in the <text styleclass="Interface">graphic-area</text> to add <text styleclass="Interface">Nodes</text> that define the shape of the <text styleclass="Element">Spline</text>.</para>
